Enable the Mac OS X outer sandbox in standalone sel_ldr

Use the sandbox_init() API to enable an outer sandbox, based on what
Chromium uses.

This has two benefits:
 * Prevents regressions of NaCl in the Chromium sandbox.
 * Makes the standalone plugin more secure.

We make NaClAclBypassChecks (i.e. file access mode) non-static so that
we can check it before enabling the sandbox.

BUG=http://code.google.com/p/nativeclient/issues/detail?id=127
TEST=existing tests

